<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>무모한 남매들</title>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <script type="text/javascript" src=//code.jquery.com/jquery-3.2.1.min.js></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/mypage_change_pw.css">

</head>
<body>
       <!-- header 시작 -->
       <header class="header">
        <!--해더내용 시작(header_all)-->
        <div class="header_index">
            <div class="header_all">
                <!-- 로고(header_all_logo) -->
                <div class="header_all_logo">
                    <a href="/"><img src="../img/logo2.jpg" alt="로고이미지"></a>
                </div>
                <!-- 검색(header_all_search) -->
                <div class="header_all_search">
                    <input class="header_search_text" type="text" placeholder="h I n 당신의 가구를 검색해 보세요.">
                    <button class="header_search_button">검색</button>
                </div>

                <!-- 햄버거 메뉴(header_left_tab) -->
                <div class="header_tab">
                    <!--햄버거 메뉴-->
                    <div class="header_left_tab">
                        <div class="header_all_tab">
                            <input class="burger-check" type="checkbox" id="burger-check" />
                            <label class="burger-icon" for="burger-check"><span class="burger-sticks"></span></label>
                            
                            <div class="menu">
                                <div style="width: 250px;">
                                    <ul>
                                        <%-login_status[0].logout %>
                                        <%-login_status[0].user_info %>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div> 
                    </div> <!--햄버거 메뉴 끝-->
                </div> <!--header_tab-->
            </div>
        </div>

        <!--네비내용 시작(nav) -->
        <div class="nav">
            <div class="nav_main">
                <li><a href="/views/store?categori=10" class="nav_link">거실</a></li>
                <li><a href="/views/store?categori=23" class="nav_link">침실</a></li>
                <li><a href="/views/store?categori=22" class="nav_link">서재</a></li>
                <li><a href="/views/store?categori=15" class="nav_link">주방</a></li>
                <li><a href="/views/store?categori=17" class="nav_link">옷방</a></li>
                <li><a href="#" class="nav_link">욕실</a></li>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header> <!--header 끝-->

    <form action="/views/mypage/mypage_change_pw" method="post" onsubmit="return change_pw()">
        <div class="contents">
                <div class="change_info_box">
                    <div class="join_pw">
                        <h3 class="join_title"><label for="new_pw">새 비밀번호</label></h3>
                        <span class="box int_pw">
                            <input type="password" id="new_pw" class="int" maxlength="14" name="pw" placeholder="8~14자,영문,숫자,특수문자 포함">
                        </span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="join_pw_check">
                        <h3 class="join_title"><label for="new_pw_check">새 비밀번호 확인</label></h3>
                        <span class="box int_pw_check">
                            <input type="password" id="new_pw_check" class="int" maxlength="14" name="pw_check" placeholder="새 비밀번호를 한번더 입력해주세요.">
                        </span>

                    </div>
                    <input type="submit" id="send_pw_btn" value="변경 하기">
                </div>
        </div>
    </form>

    <!--footer 시작-->
    <div id="footer">
        <h2>1234-1234</h2>
        <p>평일 09:00~18:00 (주말 & 공휴일 제외)
        <br/><br/>브랜드 스토리&emsp;회사소개&emsp;채용정보&emsp;이용약관&emsp;개인정보처리방침&emsp;공지사항&emsp;고객의 소리&emsp;전문가 등록&emsp;사업자 구매회원
        <br/><br/>상호명: (주)HIN&emsp;이메일: hin@ansan.ac.kr&emsp;팀원: 윤상규, 홍의주, 김태은, 안현빈&emsp;사업자등록번호: 123-456-789
        <br/><br/>주소: 경기도 안산시 상록구 안산대학로 155</p>
    </div>

    <script type="text/javascript" src="../script/change_pw.js"></script>
</body>
</html>